pcoming 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris on behalf of China.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 496, \"end\": 501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994925648403, \"rank\": 5.074354845622933e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9198187472574498, \"rank\": 0.08629933445469341, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be Jiang's first appearance at the Olympics, but she's not necessarily a stranger to Olympic-level competition, having served as a training partner for Chinese national team members Wei Meng and Zhang Donglian before the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Olympics in 2021, where Wei secured the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5520446561494071, \"rank\": 0.8092141272415404, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wei_Meng\", \"score\": 0.9999947964785275, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wei Meng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wei_Meng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wei_Meng\"}, {\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Donglian\", \"score\": 0.9999842883634862, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhang Donglian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Donglian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Donglian\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.179489958245111e-13, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 799, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Wei\", \"score\": 0.9998382039073447, \"rank\": 0.00013342405215220995, \"text\": \"Wei\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Wei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cao_Wei\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was a training partner with the Chinese national team before the Tokyo Olympics,\\\" Jiang told the China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 865, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5520446561494071, \"rank\": 0.8092141272415404, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9222803090044607, \"rank\": 0.07990296331128434, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was basically learning from the big brothers and sisters during that time to improve myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Training alongside the country's top shooters was a great help for Jiang, who began to make her name known at domestic competitions in the ensuing years.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In early 2023, she finished the World Cup trials in first place.\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gained the most from competing in the final,\\\" Jiang said.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For example, I began to understand what I should think of on break, as well as how to change my mindset to perform well in the final.\\\"\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jiang was confirmed as a member of the Chinese national team for the Paris Olympics after the International Shooting Sport Federation World Cup in Italy in June.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1510, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5520446561494071, \"rank\": 0.8092141272415404, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Shooting_Sport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Shooting Sport Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Shooting_Sport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Shooting_Sport_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9576309486688317, \"rank\": 0.03147121652674459, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIS_Alpine_Ski_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.585769603921139, \"rank\": 0.5300153400123028, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few years ago, she was a young fan of Chinese Olympians.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9458723315290133, \"rank\": 0.03221525518549929, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now she has joined their ranks.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel proud of myself for being able to compete at the Olympic Games for the first time in my career,\\\" Jiang said.\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope I can reach top-six at the event.\\\"\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\",